{"tid":1779234,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗慶祝TIME選咗依條臭雞出嚟，希望各位手足做五件事支持環保","createTime":"2019-12-11T13:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T15:53:42.000Z","uid":134997,"like":56,"dislike":212,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"dbd244b287e0e1f08e5c3061997a5007fc3edf05","tid":1779234,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T13:57:24.000Z","msg":"我承諾以後：<br />\n1. 冬天我會將個冷氣調轉嚟裝 一嚟可以向外吹冷風 減輕全球暖化 二嚟向內吹暖風 可以當暖爐用<br />\n2. 膠飲管會慢性插死海龜 基於人道考慮 所以我一罐可樂會用三枝即棄鐵飲管 務求令海龜以最快速度死亡<br />\n3. 因為一個重用水樽要用大量嘅膠/金屬 製造過程會增加碳排放 例如Polycarbonate加工溫度要上到310度 所以後會用返收縮率達70%嘅即棄膠樽 愛護環境你我有責<br />\n4. 堂食完嘅碟要用水洗 但非洲好多小朋友水都無水飲 用清水洗碗係對佢地嘅侮辱 而且過濾水要用大量chemicals 會污染海洋 所以我會嗌外賣再堂食 減少用水<br />\n5. 有人想知再講"},{"pid":"a0ebaf2f192379ffa8e6ad66a37f11f184e0f08a","tid":1779234,"uid":306738,"like":71,"dislike":11,"score":60,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:00:24.000Z","msg":"除左表現無體育精神<br />\n對場運動有咩幫助？"},{"pid":"a68727f66c616495cf69d15a5c28c2e4087b031d","tid":1779234,"uid":29080,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:01:18.000Z","msg":"以後唔戴膠笠了"},{"pid":"25db320b95d98bcb799f062824e683635959ec5a","tid":1779234,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:02:25.000Z","msg":"努力打好國際線<br />\n今日香港都成為美加焦點<br />\n<br />\n 【Twitter要人!!】美加議員人權日tweet集合list!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1779138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1779138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">需要人入去推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter 需要大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"051b0f018f8668c67d52429ffded61be185897cc","tid":1779234,"uid":134997,"like":12,"dislike":19,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"a0ebaf2f192379ffa8e6ad66a37f11f184e0f08a","tid":1